Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp

Interface JSPElementVisitor

All Known Implementing Classes:
JSPCodeGenerator
public interface JSPElementVisitor
Visitor interface for processing JSP elements using the visitor pattern. This enables various operations on the JSP abstract syntax tree such as code generation, validation, and transformation.

Implementations of this interface can traverse the JSP AST and perform specific operations on each element type without modifying the element classes themselves.

Author:
Chris Burdess
